videos.description: Deandre Ayton times the rebound of a missed 3-pointer and gets the putback dunk for Arizona.
videos.headline: Ayton gets rebound for putback slam

videos.description: David Crisp gets out quickly and finishes strong with the left hand to put the Huskies up 23-16.
videos.headline: Washington's Crisp elevates for fastbreak layup

videos.description: Deandre Ayton races to the hoop in transition and winds up for the big dunk.
videos.headline: Ayton launches for monster dunk

videos.description: Matisse Thybulle races by Deandre Ayton and goes up for the reverse slam putting Washington up 30-22.
videos.headline: Thybulle hits reverse dunk for Huskies

videos.description: Alonzo Trier lifts off for the one-handed jam as the lane opens up for him.
videos.headline: Trier flies through lane for dunk

videos.description: Noah Dickerson splits two defenders and reaches out for the scoop and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: Dickerson extends for the Washington and-1

videos.description: Deandre Ayton denies Sam Timmins and outlets to Allonzo Trier who goes up strong for the and-1 layup cutting Washington's lead to 50-48.
videos.headline: Ayton block leads to Trier and-1

videos.description: Allonzo Trier pulls up off the screen and is fouled by David Crisp to pull off the four-point play.
videos.headline: Trier knocks down a 3 and draws foul

videos.description: Dominic Green collects the ball in the corner after a hectic sequence and knocks down a three-pointer to tie it at 73-73.
videos.headline: Green ties it with corner 3 for Washington

videos.description: Deandre Ayton's block falls to Dominic Green, who knocks down a buzzer-beating 3-pointer with a second left to take down No. 9 Arizona.
videos.headline: Green takes down Arizona at the buzzer
